    Interface Description
    FIRE
    Interface FIRE specifies requirements for 5COM2007 Cwk 3 - Nov 2022.
  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    BenchTesting
    Tests the Island and Ferry classes.
    BusinessPass
    A BusinessPass extends the Pass class to add a loyalty points field which is increased every time a pass uses the ferry and can be exchanged for credits.
    EmployeePass
    An EmployeePass extends the Pass class to add a job description and an employee number.
    Ferry
    A ferry provides a one-way journey between two islands.
    Island
    An island is part of a FIRE resort.
    Pass
    A Pass represents a person in the resort who has an id number, a name, a luxury rating, a certain number of credits, and a certain amount of journey points.
    PassTester
    Tests the Pass class.
    Resort
    This class implements the FIRE interface.
    ResortUI
    Provides an interface to the user allowing them to create and manage a resort.
    Teamwork
    Details of your pair
    Tester
    Tests the Resort class through the ResortUI class.
    TouristPass
    A TouristPass extends the Pass class to add a citizenship field and an increased cost for the ferry.
